711
00:56:05,169 --> 00:56:07,308
Perhatikan langkahmu.

712
00:56:07,308 --> 00:56:08,937
Ya. Maaf.

713
00:57:04,044 --> 00:57:05,301
Ini ongkosnya.

714
00:57:07,594 --> 00:57:08,694
Tapi.

715
00:57:09,841 --> 00:57:11,208
Kenapa tanda pengenalnya bisa hilang?

716
00:57:11,208 --> 00:57:12,469
Entah.

717
00:57:16,721 --> 00:57:19,197
Tanda pengenalku hilang.

718
00:57:20,837 --> 00:57:22,601
<i>[Park Dong Hoon]</i>

719
00:57:28,496 --> 00:57:31,158
