924
01:14:17,359 --> 01:14:19,560
Kau tak ada niat mau
pacaran sungguhan sama dia?

925
01:14:32,711 --> 01:14:33,907
Apa sekarang ini...

926
01:14:34,702 --> 01:14:36,020
...kau.../
Hubungan yang tidak wajar...

927
01:14:36,020 --> 01:14:38,358
